data.title: Life Member Honor Roll :: USF Alumni Association
data.meta_description: Alumni Association Life Membership represents a deep commitment to USF and our mission to advance our university by providing Bulls with meaningful ways to make a positive impact.
data.text:
Thank you, Life Members, Circle of Excellence donors and U Club donors.

Alumni Association Life Membership represents a deep commitment to USF and our mission to advance our university by providing Bulls with meaningful ways to make a positive impact. We gratefully acknowledge all of our Life Members (as of Dec. 31, 2023) and recognize your generous contributions.

In our Circle of Excellence, we recognize Life Members who made additional unrestricted annual gifts in 2023, as well as all 28 donors in the prestigious University Club. U Club alumni and friends have made a significant impact on USF through endowments of $25,000 or more.

Your generosity allows us to continue to connect Bulls to one another and our school so we can share our pride, stay connected, protect USF, and help our great university continue to succeed.
